prompts.frontCover: A humorous dreamy fantasy illustration of a funny birthday scene. Lao Lao (woman from photo) and Jordan (man from photo), transformed into charming cartoon characters, are reacting with dramatic, playful shock. They are wearing mismatched, whimsical party hats that sparkle faintly. They kneel on a floor made of swirling, soft-focus pastel clouds, reaching out desperately. Their focus is a tiny, fluffy Corgi puppy who is victoriously trotting away, carrying a comically oversized slice of pepperoni pizza that's bigger than it is. The pizza drips magical, glittering cheese onto the cloud floor. In the background, an open pizza box sits on a patch of ethereal green grass, with glowing mushrooms and tiny, sparkling fireflies floating around it. The overall color palette is soft lavender, rose quartz, and mint green, creating a magical, ethereal atmosphere. Centered in a safe area, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script using a shimmering gold color. The artwork is flat 2D with clean lines and soft, blended colors, perfect for a greeting card.
